DESCRIPTION:Come prepared to engage\, reflect\, and discover how personal transformation shapes the way you lead transformation in others.\n\nWhat to Expect:\n- Interactive learning and discussion\n- A practical definition of transformation in leadership\n- Personal reflection exercises\n- Practical leadership insights\n- Live Q&A\n- Introduction to the ROOTED leadership journey\n\n## Rooted Cohort\nIf you wish to go even deeper with us we are running a Rooted Cohort for leaders wanting to qualify as personal coaches.\nVisit: https://lftleadership.com/rooted\n\nJoin Zoom Meeting: https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86312144391?pwd=NoSGKPYaUrDi5MCAC93sLiGgJUoNvB.1
